The Premier League returns, after Champions League and Europa League fixtures in midweek. On Sunday, Norwich City host out-of-sorts Arsenal in the early game, while Sheffield United travel to Wolves. Leicester City, who are in second place, welcome Everton. Manchester United take on Aston Villa in the last game of the weekend. Sunday, December 1
15:00 Norwich City vs Arsenal
15:00 Wolverhampton Wanderers vs Sheffield United
17:30 Leicester City vs Everton
